pageContext.claim: “@CBS and their show, @60Minutes, are doing everything within their power, which is far less today than it was in the past, to defend China and the horrible Virus pandemic that was inflicted on the USA and the rest of the World. I guess they want to do business in China!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has chafed at hard-hitting reports on "60 Minutes" into his administration's halting response to the covid-19 outbreak. But there's no basis for his claim that the newsmagazine's reporting is meant "to defend China" or the pandemic.
